OL,3,CFour-fifths of UK firms impacted by
OL,4,CIran war fallout ` report
OL,6,FEight in 10 UK firms are suffering a
OL,7,Fhit from the Iran war and a fifth of
OL,8,Fbusinesses are putting investment
OL,9,Fplans on hold because of the
OL,10,Fgeopolitical uncertainty, according to
OL,11,Fa report.
OL,13,FThe latest Barclays Business
OL,14,FProsperity index revealed 80% of UK
OL,15,Fbusinesses reported a negative impact
OL,16,Ffrom the Middle East conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
