OL,3,CFour-fifths of UK firms impacted by
OL,4,CIran war fallout ` report
OL,6,FMore than two-thirds (64%) said energy
OL,7,Fand fuel costs were impacting on their
OL,8,Fbusiness, with 34% hit by higher
OL,9,Fshipping and logistics costs and a
OL,10,Fthird suffering supply chain
OL,11,Fdisruption, the report found.
OL,13,FIn a sign of the knock-on effect on
OL,14,Fconsumers, 37% of the 1,000 senior
OL,15,Fcompany decision makers surveyed for
OL,16,Fthe report between April 17 and May 5
OL,17,Fsaid they expect to pass on cost hikes
OL,18,Fto customers through higher prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
