PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779847405
OL,3,CFour-fifths of UK firms impacted by
OL,4,CIran war fallout ` report
OL,6,FMr Hammerstein called for an AI role
OL,7,Fto be created at the highest level of
OL,8,Fgovernment, given the marked shift
OL,9,Ftowards AI and Britain's desire to be
OL,10,Fat the forefront of the new technology.
OL,12,FHe said: "AI is now a defining driver
OL,13,Fof productivity and global
OL,14,Fcompetitiveness, so elevating AI
OL,15,Fministerial responsibility to Cabinet
OL,16,Flevel would send a clear signal of the
OL,17,FUK's strategic intent.
OL,26,@tD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779847405
OL,3,CFour-fifths of UK firms impacted by
OL,4,CIran war fallout ` report
OL,6,F"With a cross-cutting mandate to set
OL,7,Fstrategy, co-ordinate departments,
OL,8,Flead industry engagement and oversee
OL,9,Fcrisis response, this would strengthen
OL,10,Fauthority without duplication and
OL,11,Fposition the UK to better capture the
OL,12,Feconomic opportunities of AI as a
OL,13,Fglobal hub for innovation and growth."
OL,15,FResults of the lender's survey
OL,16,Fsuggests investment in AI is paying
OL,17,Foff, with 52% of firm saying they
OL,18,Fbelieve AI and automation has improved
OL,19,Ftheir productivity, with 38% saying
OL,20,Femployees now spend less time on
OL,21,Fadministrative tasks.
